Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Introducing "The Cloisters" 200 St Georges Tce, one of Perth CBDs  most vibrant,  energy-conscious A Grade commercial buildings located at the West end of the Perth CBD.

After a recent major refurbishment, the building flaunts slick amenities and energy-saving initiatives to support premium tenants & their clients. 

These include;

- New building lobby and concierge
- Premium grade end of trip facilities & health centre
- Excellent private and public parking
- Direct connection to Perth's No. 1 retail food court 
- Onsite Management 
- 4.5 Star NABERS rating

The owner takes great pride in this complex with a focus on the health and well-being of all their customers. 

Current leasing opportunities include;

Level 2 - 530m2 | Refurbished open plan

Level 5 - 1100m2 | Brand new spec fitout (See virtual tour 1)

Level 6 - 1100m2 | Fully refurbished open plan

Level 8 - 530m2 | Quality existing fitout

Level 10 - 530m2 | Fully refurbished open plan


The complex is immaculately maintained with an ongoing CAPEX programme and fitout strategy ensuring all current vacancies are presented to the highest standard. 

For more information please contact the exclusive leasing agents CBRE and JLL.
